WEBVTT

00:01:28.058 --> 00:01:30.740
of telling all of our stories equally.

00:01:31.491 --> 00:01:35.287
Too often, we see the building
of monuments like the Gherkin

00:01:35.311 --> 00:01:36.692
or even Trump Tower ...

00:01:36.716 --> 00:01:38.358
(Laughter)

00:01:38.749 --> 00:01:42.257
that tell the story of the haves
rather than the have-nots.

00:01:43.245 --> 00:01:45.013
Throughout my career,

00:01:45.037 --> 00:01:46.708
I've actively resisted the practice

00:01:46.732 --> 00:01:49.657
of building monuments
to certain peoples' stories --

00:01:49.681 --> 00:01:53.023
usually white, male, rich --

00:01:53.047 --> 00:01:55.512
and bulldozing other peoples' stories --

00:01:55.536 --> 00:01:57.235
usually people of color

00:01:57.259 --> 00:01:58.729
from low-income communities.

00:01:59.857 --> 00:02:01.334
